# Documentation Standard

## Living record

- Never rewrite historical Changelog entries — **append only**.
- Preserve chronological history.
- Separate Canon from Recommendations.
- Documentation reflects approved decisions and inspected/implemented truth — do not invent APIs.

## Required touchpoints (gameplay missions)

- Mission doc under `Documents/05_Missions/`
- `Documents/04_Production/Changelog.md` (append)
- Architecture / systems docs only if ownership, APIs, or dependencies changed
- `ProjectHealth.md` / Roadmap when project status changes
- Mission Completion Report (Contribution Guide format)

## Process authority

Production process: `Documents/04_Production/ProductionPlaybook.md`.  
AI Studio map: `Documents/04_Production/AIStudio/README.md`.

## Honesty

- Record PENDING_USER / human-gated Gameplay PASS clearly.
- Tag deferred debt in mission Notes and TechnicalDebt when new.
- Do not claim Complete / Ready For Review when docs diverge from the build.
